snippet.title: VOIDBORN - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2072660/Voidborn
Follow the development: https://twitter.com/Xekvera
Demo coming August 2022.

Voidborn is a fast-paced roguelite FPS that combines skill-based action and swift movement with roguelike level progression and character customization. Rip apart demons with devastating weapon builds and reach as far as possible before you inevitably perish and become reborn stronger than ever.

Music by David Steinmarck(Relinquishr)
